From 2afa27bbffc41bf4fc3ab139f9cb1187ae6d5117 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ren Wang <iamwrm@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:48:40 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] Integrate ChatGPT Codex Responses transport

Add the chatgpt_oauth auth scheme, live bearer and account-header
resolution, and the complete Codex request and SSE response contract.
Normalize assistant history, exclude unsigned display-only reasoning, and
preserve streamed text, reasoning summaries, and function calls when the
backend omits assembled terminal output. This supports first turns,
resumed conversations, and multi-loop local tool execution without false
empty-response retries.
